Package: learnitdashboard
Type: Package
Version: 1.0.1
Title: Shiny Dashboard for 'learnitr' Data
Description: A dashboard to explore data generated by 'learnitr' code, such
  as the 'learnitdown', or the 'learnitgrid' R package. This is a lightweight
  learning analytics solution for the 'learnitr' ecosystem.
